are going down. And what is coming up?  Even we have lots of these

00:19:32.459 --> 00:19:36.542
people in India, panditas, and shastras and this and that,

00:19:36.999 --> 00:19:40.334
they don't know anything I would say, because unless and until

00:19:40.834 --> 00:19:45.459
they feel the Paramchaitanya, their all talking is baseless.

00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:51.459
So all these problems which are created by fighting,

00:19:51.751 --> 00:19:56.334
by aggressiveness, showing off or whatever you may call,

00:19:56.751 --> 00:19:58.834
can be corrected with Sahaja Yoga

00:19:58.999 --> 00:20:01.334
because your attention goes beyond the mind.

00:20:02.959 --> 00:20:04.834
You go beyond the mind.

