This Agnya chakra opens and you go beyond the mind

00:20:08.542 --> 00:20:10.834
and then you are one with this divine power.

00:20:11.292 --> 00:20:13.459
Once you are one with the divine power,

00:20:13.667 --> 00:20:18.167
how it works for you in small, small ways.

