you are all Sahaja Yogis so I need not tell you,

00:20:22.751 --> 00:20:27.709
but everyone can tell so many examples, by which

00:20:28.167 --> 00:20:31.667
he knows that it's the Paramchaitanya which has worked it.

00:20:32.459 --> 00:20:37.042
So first and foremost thing of every seeker of truth

00:20:37.292 --> 00:20:41.375
who is a real person, is to first get Self-Realization.

00:20:41.876 --> 00:20:45.626
That is the essence of spirituality, all over the world,

00:20:45.876 --> 00:20:48.417
even if you read Bible, if you read Koran.

00:20:48.584 --> 00:20:51.709
Nobody has read them that's the best part of it.

00:20:51.918 --> 00:20:55.709
And they are trying to say things which are very shameful.

