00:24:14.626 --> 00:24:17.999
definitely very constructive, very helpful,

00:24:18.459 --> 00:24:21.417
and peace giving, and harmony giving to the whole society.

00:24:22.334 --> 00:24:24.792
But first of all it has to be within you.

00:24:24.999 --> 00:24:27.999
If it is not within you, how can you give it to others.

00:24:28.626 --> 00:24:32.792
I've been watching how Sahaja Yoga has grown from one person

00:24:32.999 --> 00:24:34.667
to all these, so many of them.

