So, just imagine how simple it has become.

00:26:14.999 --> 00:26:18.459
How simple it is for Me. At this age I can't go

00:26:18.709 --> 00:26:20.792
to seventy, eighty countries,

00:26:20.999 --> 00:26:23.542
but it has passed there, it has gone there.

00:26:23.751 --> 00:26:27.834
It has given the blessings of the Divine.

